# Puzzle Java Assignment

## Description
A Java program that uses the Random class to generate random numbers, random letters, random passwords, and shuffle array values.

## Files

PuzzleJava.java
TestPuzzleJava.java

## Features

- Generate 10 random numbers (1-20)
- Generate a random letter
- Generate an 8-character password
- Generate multiple passwords
- Shuffle an array (Bonus)

## How to Run

1. Open Eclipse
2. Run TestPuzzleJava.java
3. View output in the Console

## Technologies

- Java
- Eclipse IDE
- ArrayList
- Random Class